Last year, I was mixed with my orientation. For me, it was difficulted to choice a vocation at only 18 yeas old. Effectively, before when I was a children, I have some dreams like become veterinary or high level sportswoman. But growing up, I was interested by the fashion. Because I love luxury clothing, those that overflow with extragence. The conception of the clothing, the organization of a fashion week, the creativity of peoples who creates and elaborates much of pieces. Yes, I am interesting for some things. You will ask why she don't go in a school of fashion ? Itook the steps for this kind of school, but the expectations are very picky and it is not enough to be interested but especially to know how to create, to have more inspiration. And the price was too high.
So, I went in Information and Communication, because some peoples, talk about this track. They said, it's more interesting, and it can open for you in events. So, after I didn't hesitated to go in Information and Communication. Because I would like become fashion week organizer or at least having a link with the fashion, anything that can bring me closer to fashion, would please me more.
 This webpage performs keylogging of input typed into a textbox. In other words, when focused on the textbox below, the page will record each time you hit a key or select text with your mouse. All of the data is stored locally on your machine in the DOM and is downloadable as s JSON file. More information about the motivation of this project and the format of the produced data are available here.
